lnktCOJyP5xnlduHiM2YU2oouAfDP__d86ugqYA7y9vt7O7xQ/LJxnbWDxcnAzKLQ5862_yJMoGUuxyAf_/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="德意志银行称中国是战争时代的能源“赢家”"&gt;使中国变得更加强大&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt; “从经济角度、能源结构角度来看，中国是这场战争的赢家，”他在接受采访时表示。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure style="margin: 20px 0;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/0APluS_ExstJEU7LLbdjR1bNeURc-Y6pWDqjPVoWQwRMtJ_6e9p4aOaAbjMFTtlV6wzaUvTvZEaIqCHMCXmHXsKaMFjYNyaRDnGYCO7V4WjD1Q8F_LMdfB6AlE6skmCaMFKTfp6vctgU72aghuc5zQtvVYHrV1W6zR8GNduEWiXuSMRjrZOrym_v5auGSE04BbPO7evdTtURntI94pJZSqoeLwm31GWYqvszzKhCMIzEtjiaIVSXNBKGVFKFKSVxdDSynAseGyD5wrOX2Co6IFzzPtDfc8q-JdWsG06x3WqPFKAj6I3gdr87YuTPSDHh4zvmrC1DEq_xp6FM1Jzp2m6wFz8xMJ_v75ZEBPUSwqu9sH30luZZfcYkhsI3K28v7wXYRUF0rhhIyy0H/9uuf_Ta90c0aBToj3Dl78xspjtM4eMyR/19" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iEpworvSBh2M/v11/-1x-1.jpg" alt="The production line manufacturing solar panels at the Hanwha Solutions Corp. Q Cells Division factory in Jincheon, Chungcheongbuk province, South Korea, on Wednesday, Oct. 12, 2022. South Korean clean-energy companies are major foreign winners from Washington’s landmark climate law as they benefit from tax credits and a turn away from China. Hanwha Solutions Corp., a solar equipment maker with manufacturing and research sites in North America, said it’s expecting to get more than $200 million in tax credits annually from next year. Photographer: SeongJoon Cho&amp;amp;#x2F;Bloomberg" width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="2022 年 10 月 12 日星期三，韩国忠清北道镇川市韩华解决方案公司 Q Cells 部门工厂的生产线正在生产太阳能电池板。韩国清洁能源公司是华盛顿具有里程碑意义的气候法的主要外国赢家，因为它们受益于税收抵免和远离中国。韩华解决方案公司是一家在北美设有制造和研究基地的太阳能设备制造商，该公司表示，预计从明年起每年将获得超过 2 亿美元的税收抵免。摄影师：SeongJoon Cho&amp;amp;#x2F;Bloomberg" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iEpworvSBh2M/v11/-1x-1.jpg" style="width: 100%; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4;"&gt;中国的太阳能电池板制造&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4; font-style: italic;"&gt;摄影师：SeongJoon Cho/彭博社&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;这一预测形成了一幅复杂的图景。智&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/FEGy2aV8xbyi9z6vDYqG0AmquwN6gJLp9rhSAINEj8RuippmBFxxOOA0CicT_0zN3s79fkrtEmA57Zux5hwvmymWE3780XTS4qpvlfNt2toZishT-O49Cqzn4tbNWwXqZQSSvt8VK1L3pEW9i5NGY1I0lUIxUT8ik99oS0xxfXCsTGqhbJBCd0oodbILqnMiRrqu-H-X2D1Jqf_Afk9_-B4XZgN1zUZYX98yodEa1ERztAsA46AE2tiEnxOpMiJaks2cSx8TPq_EkPxH4zQYPNl6KBCUBydWNMy7fkor6b8AUJEg0sYAtafUEnds2peJ0yGW9Qnd6jU8Ef3ipkbaW9Px4XG5IHR5efiRV2FIsbsDxk7BsKCkCsVarqPNwjfyyqkk85gOFDfatQ1m5LyxNWj_NxvJMy1KS5-LRIzZa8KkrWOzNln1d3t7iWx4gJu2_Ps/et9Qptt1bNYrZcKFVDljMsi4xAsAX-mF/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="勃鲁盖尔AISBL"&gt;库布鲁盖尔&lt;/a&gt;表示，中国对伊朗石油进口的依赖将对其能源战略构成“ &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/wUeKCW32wuz_2HIYb38z3i2ANuQV5bbe_xVmpXkb6ggCgC7vlGUlY23r2ozU2vc1ulbqvVQwdd4yJlxjeQrSJ2IfhX3Tw4tTsfBiU46Rjq44Nhgxjna2JqKhZnkGY3hxEnSEdvwgJdQfML2X-A-hAfzMU8pd145u6Q_PWydheVl9wwWb-MitG3-5Stal_0OA0UgGGr4BaVz_KG7OfydQsTQd98NPZWfvAhk6x4dveVm727wBvzr5hUx9u2kBU1CkfybVvs0TWUtQ-RdXGbS9Jxzf8stYBiSVaw_82wl3MRlFNzCknvuJ05UURIfq0EqnuIhNRh5wvQ/OWPr0qZ8fjETKgt5z2mJ5yIVAOVUwmgL/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="伊朗战争对中国意味着什么"&gt;严峻考验&lt;/a&gt;”。与此同时，德意志银行高管表示，该国作为全球最大的清洁技术生产国的地位使其处于独特的地位，可以帮助各国政府摆脱对中东进口的依赖。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;唐说，从长远来看，“每个人都知道”世界“不能依赖石油”。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure style="margin: 20px 0;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/BRojdx5u7In4Nl3XMEjU7dTS-zWkhBZaxej17BvR_1Ji6tnG2b3g6XMS-6tkzT6XaW3ZrVwvGY5ZpkY3DkNjeTCPwYp1wCrdufj0qnju0X_rrsrggEbhGPrirNlnLgAUycubpGwp3QtAhMUJXFuUFLDz1y7l4jAuZNA8mba2bBCjNUn6cEgOUJxIDKYBoc6zjq_LqcjfVKjgibf05hY0e-g0iOsslOXzY3S6K0xpvarO4kIqPXWENZL11xJ9n9tXZQu1g6vdHuamVnZM_9K4ajaMOSlnTQI3QIHG-NvKxiL6abOBHTOqi09Bm-4ips_WHuRzi_omy1X3ZxkpfP-ZRc_3JkNAkCtlHYCagAwL8MksItlryOI0fQUFSixAjP51heR89jzLOfWYYPBP/I3ChohSqUWy84C-5NEj0YYZCJKlqIz0s/19" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iVsDibWZ0uDc/v8/-1x-1.jpg" alt="Smoke rises after an explosion in the industrial zone in Fujairah, United Arab Emirates, on Tuesday, March 3, 2026. Oil surged for a second day as the US and Israel stepped up their war against Iran, with a fire at a key storage hub in the United Arab Emirates underscoring the risk to energy supplies. Source: Bloomberg" width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="2026 年 3 月 3 日星期二，阿拉伯联合酋长国富查伊拉工业区发生爆炸后冒出浓烟。随着美国和以色列加大对伊朗的战争力度，油价连续第二天飙升，阿拉伯联合酋长国一个重要存储中心发生火灾，凸显了能源供应面临的风险。资料来源：彭博社" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iVsDibWZ0uDc/v8/-1x-1.jpg" style="width: 100%; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4;"&gt;阿拉伯联合酋长国富查伊拉工业区发生爆炸后冒出浓烟。&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4; font-style: italic;"&gt;资料来源：彭博社&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;他表示，这一认识将迫使亚洲这个中东石油最大进口国进行调整。唐说，日本、韩国和印度现在更有可能寻求能源结构多元化的方法，而实现这种多元化所需的设备将不可避免地来自中国。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;随着中东冲突在生存威胁和脆弱的停火之间摇摆不定，石油和天然气价格的波动性急剧上升。周三早上， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/Kz8eNtblW00iXCztECpRB5bGmh7G8_fRmx0MYcEpB9Hn8crkM8XQMQaQR