。即使霍尔木兹海峡有望重新开放，世界各地的石油和天然气价格仍然上涨，我们开始看到对当地经济的影响，特别是亚洲的经济。本周，彭博社观点专栏作家戴维·菲克林 (David Fickling) 在《零》节目中解释了这些影响是什么，以及它们将如何在未来几十年重塑亚洲的能源系统。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;立即收听，并在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/BbkTT8MhFvz8JeKsuZXkfwomG6qSQXTAXKvHa_6IGWr8X11NnEGprDOdJ8EYjI9fDk-u9_sHIsrZYjtL5aAUs59sKmtCtbNtMIxbEpRI3v4V9C-A0jEBCzVKG3BUe_zMZiFIegGXY9OZgaKyhi2kGqyVX2c-d4fxxtElZ0d43LbgDw1xDTdURx6EKxl7___vf58JWjfl3Fx3QD8MUeTEvA4mmsg670Qr1NsY3TscL0leWcF_TWCgGP4k-Zai0JfbibZkiQrJV7yMPTByAOr6VMAJ3gzeP8qFkrSLZnpn4r7aYUXaiq9l-7Tuoruu7INoorU6Xg/NVJ4-qZ4Z-AyZqbJ7Gq7kJwQz0rOwSpW/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="零：气候竞赛"&gt;Apple&lt;/a&gt; 、 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/YcDgIVW8gqN-i57xLP-2i6sAfhaBudGGgA0xcYbUuKsy2wSn5u0XdRyAg5IUoDxCj7f-ihc3AX5AkXx0HyE7kn98R6y21uuIAPSb803tj4gZgkUHHoZvaNn952WeVgGo6xyqScuWpW_-Suj1SRBrn-40tQhsaBxEcFhEoY6xJIBbGwPj7qdO0LR_jGGE1lKZ6FwYBkrqMsyf93CIvCnYCdSaY0ZTYqHAoVwnTepWkLgLFea9XDba100MP7yyIplXRTPeylRFKI90qDcv0POA1t1QPtu1WuMH51_B8VZHguQh4lE9kaFeHfNoAin2wkab3rfL0ZP6f53WRMElq61jDCWWGVzk/rHOB_WXhiYEGjKfDiTk7V9ifCUDFq3jo/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="零：气候竞赛"&gt;Spotify&lt;/a&gt;或&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/7YZ_CWjSTvF0MZvUMgyp1xmunKEgoLQ_DDI5jHbZEw3PNrv-2roWwIRELXUWIZ1h5HbR_HK0bd_ZZNhjubZzpYBR0qTHScaBJEhYgYN-L2e1KPFJiapZrEIAPI9b2KSaxjLtG_rHlTUBeIW6AVKdo3lSXLVYmr58ORaOqnDbUegJCrTBbw8J7DCuPNbcjgn67kM-9zv0v3w5lI6mRhf_Xv6NyquFl-6LSL1MpDCX42SED-iIrI1RBADBihcyjzI8ZNsNhmPQMbMx3hmoLUoHbb5tMafvLrky9-d30SwDkiWDn4pdAdqivvwuao4hrFgqO2XtEvf38vC-h-UjULvEp7KQ4hH3/U1CHJWOF8EZ77Qg4iLbiurUbgK3QioAl/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="零：气候竞赛"&gt;YouTube&lt;/a&gt;上订阅，即可每周四观看《零》的新剧集。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-t