F9VnRfPhYyRAs7lRY0liUIL/gTPoH21u5zMwX4Oe8bVukDtiLFyQlbsv/19" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iTCXWNEktDYQ/v12/-1x-1.jpg" alt="Neal Kumar, chief legal officer of Polymarket, center left, uses an electronic Polymarket display during the opening of The Situation Room by Polymarket pop-up bar in Washington, DC, US, on Friday, March 20, 2026. Polymarket took over a bar near the White House, for a promotional event showcasing the prediction market’s vision of betting on current events as a new form of entertainment. Photographer: Graeme Sloan&amp;amp;#x2F;Bloomberg" width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="2026 年 3 月 20 日星期五，Polymarket 首席法律官 Neal Kumar（中左）在美国华盛顿特区 The Situation Room by Polymarket 快闪酒吧开业期间使用 Polymarket 电子显示屏。Polymarket 接管了白宫附近的一家酒吧，举办促销活动，展示预测市场将时事投注作为一种新的娱乐形式的愿景。摄影师：格雷姆·斯隆&amp;amp;#x2F;彭博社" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iTCXWNEktDYQ/v12/-1x-1.jpg" style="width: 100%; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4;"&gt; Polymarket 首席法律官 Neal Kumar（中左）在华盛顿特区 The Situation Room by Polymarket 快闪酒吧开业期间使用 Polymarket 电子显示屏。&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4; font-style: italic;"&gt;摄影师：格雷姆·斯隆/彭博社&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;上个月，就在唐纳德·特朗普宣布美国推迟对伊朗能源基础设施进行军事打击之前，发现石油和股票期货的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/EbFpD4Lbw6MOM9IsGTvjNCUQNigpDNQmSFLsYcCsDp0b3trB2AtH8vahMkr_UqqewdfbvUexVjiFPdLBtLRTfeOoHYde68uPCuDVLO0oGMf1jhOSdsw7S8MxhZkvW5fwsn3ZXAxqcWt-Hz-y-BwHNh4AYH9OVD_RaFDY6zxze23FNyVoBrF-rvy186IdfzCqjk7v1YLl14J51QFUWDkB6oN7DnohFdxdT-nm-4-2jEv3M6NmE-GYnw8sP2PjxYtPmzgYsm4B-UB9yZnwDNFe5J-EBgN_tM